<template>
  <CiMqttLastX></CiMqttLastX>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent } from 'vue'
import { Geof } from '../classes/Geo'
import CiMqttLastX from '@/components/CiMqttLastX.vue'

export default defineComponent({
  name: 'History',
  components: {
    CiMqttLastX
  },
  computed: {
    geof: function (): Geof {
      const geo1 = new Geof(0, 0, 1, 1)
      return geo1
    },
    dx: function (): number { return (this.geof.dxo()) },
    dy: function (): number { return (this.geof.dyo()) }
  },
  methods: {
    showErdgeschoss: function () {
      console.log('CLICK - showErdgeschoss', '')
      return this.$router.push({ name: 'Erdgeschoss' })
    }
  }
})
</script>
